msgstr "首次设置"

#: src/pm-window.c:3997
msgid "Welcome to Phone Mirror"
msgstr "欢迎使用手机镜像"

#: src/pm-window.c:3998
msgid ""
"We will help you prepare your Android phone. Keep your phone nearby and "
"connect it to the same Wi-Fi network as this computer."
msgstr ""
"我们将帮助您准备 Android 手机。请将手机放在附近,并将其连接到与此计算机相同的 "
"Wi-Fi 网络。"

#: src/pm-window.c:4001
msgid "Open Settings"
msgstr "打开设置"

#: src/pm-window.c:4002
msgid "Unlock your Android phone. Find the Settings app and open it."
msgstr "解锁您的 Android 手机。找到“设置”应用并打开它。"

#: src/pm-window.c:4005
msgid "Find About phone"
msgstr "找到“关于手机”"

#: src/pm-window.c:4006
msgid ""
"In Settings, scroll toward the bottom. Tap About phone. On some phones, open "
"System first, then tap About phone."
msgstr ""
"在“设置”中向下滚动。点按“关于手机”。在某些手机上,请先打开“系统”,然后点按“关于"
"手机”。"

#: src/pm-window.c:4009
msgid "Turn on Developer options"
msgstr "开启开发者选项"

#: src/pm-window.c:4010
msgid ""
"Find Build number. Tap Build number seven times. If Android asks for your "
"PIN, enter it. Stop when the phone says you are now a developer."
msgstr ""
"找到“版本号”。点按“版本号”七次。如果 Android 要求输入 PIN,请输入。当手机提示"
"您已成为开发者时停止。"

#: src/pm-window.c:4013
msgid "Turn on USB debugging"
msgstr "开启 USB 调试"

#: src/pm-window.c:4014
msgid ""
"Go back to Settings. Open Developer options. On some phones, open System "
"first, then turn on USB debugging. If Android asks, tap OK."
msgstr ""
"返回“设置”。打开开发者选项。在某些手机上,请先打开“系统”,然后开启 USB 调试。如"
"果 Android 询问,请点按“确定”。"

#: src/pm-window.c:4018
msgid ""
"Stay in Developer options. Find Disable adb authorization timeout and turn "
"it on. This stops Android from removing this computer after seven days, so "
"you will not have to pair again."
msgstr ""
"保持在开发者选项中。找到“停用 adb 授权超时”并将其开启。这样 Android 就不会在"
"七天后移除此电脑,您也无需重新配对。"

#: src/pm-window.c:4021
msgid "Turn on Wireless debugging"
msgstr "开启无线调试"

#: src/pm-window.c:4022
msgid ""
"Stay in Developer options. Turn on Wireless debugging. Keep your phone and "
"this computer on the same network. If Android asks, tap Allow."
msgstr ""
"保持在开发者选项中。开启无线调试。让您的手机和此计算机处于同一网络。如果 "
"Android 询问,请点按“允许”。"

#: src/pm-window.c:4025
msgid "Get the pairing code"
msgstr "获取配对码"

#: src/pm-window.c:4026
msgid ""
"Tap Wireless debugging, then Pair device with pairing code. Leave that "
"screen open. On the home page, choose Set Up Device, enter the pairing "
"address and code, then choose Pair & Connect."
msgstr ""
"点按“无线调试”,然后点按“使用配对码配对设备”。保持该屏幕开启。在主页上,选择“设"
"置设备”,输入配对地址和配对码,然后选择“配对并连接”。"

#: src/pm-window.c:4040
msgid "Welcome"
msgstr "欢迎"

